
---

## 8) Commit & Push adımları (özet)
Terminalde repo kökünde:

```bash
git add system/kernel/linker.ld
git add system/kernel/main.c
git add system/boot/grub.cfg
git add system/kernel/Makefile
git add Makefile
git add .gitignore
git add README.md
git commit -m "Add real bootable kernel, linker, grub and build files"
git push origin main
sudo apt update
sudo apt install build-essential nasm grub-pc-bin xorriso qemu-system-x86
# cross-compiler istersen: x86_64-elf-gcc toolchain kurman gerekir.
make build
make iso
qemu-system-x86_64 -cdrom TeOS.iso -m 512
